snippet.title: Seekers: Enlightenment Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In this 2D Action Platformer, embark on this journey with Ivy and Lara to seek out the real truth behind this world and perhaps the world beyond filled with gods, strange creatures, different enemies as you discover new environments.


if you are interested in this game, you can wishlist now on Steam!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2486240/Seekers_Enlightenment/
